# shadcn/ui Usage

- Prefer shadcn/ui primitives: Button, Badge, Card, Table, Select, DropdownMenu over custom markup
- Use Button variants: default (primary), outline, ghost for different contexts
- Use Card, CardHeader, CardContent, CardFooter for card layouts
- Use Table components for tabular data with proper semantics
- Use Select for dropdowns; DropdownMenu for action menus
